[div class=p 
	"Mappy Arrangement is one of 6 games included in Namco Classic Collection Vol. 1 which is a compilation that was released in 1995 for Arcades. For this volume, the games are Galaga, Xevious, and Mappy. Both volumes are notable for introducing the "Arrangement" series which serve as new takes of the game named after. These often introduce new enemies & variants, a variety of level themes, boss fights, and simultaneous co-op. 
	[small 
		"This and Rally-X Arrangement are the only games that haven't gotten any rerelease at all...
	]small
	$LF
]div
