[h4 id=Strats 
	"Strats
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"While it's nothing game-breaking and the TAS still needs to have favorable RNG (where the Meowkies/pink cats go), Mappy has some strats regarding the doors and the levers.
	$LF
]div
[ul 
	[li 
		[b 
			"Short Warp:
		]b
		" If Player 1 or Player 2 closes a door/lever in a specific position, pressing left on the same frame as the second to last frame of the closing door/lever animation, they'll be able to warp to the other side which can save a few frames compared to walking.
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		[b 
			"Door Specific:
		]b
		" Opening and Closing the door and then opening it again can lead to a strange behavoir where pressing the opposite direction on the same frame as opening it (after opening and closing it once) the door will act as if the player was on the other side and will slam them into that direction instead of the intended direction. Useful for when there's a item near the door.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
